680
01:56:38,628 --> 01:56:39,928
Mana Kraven?

681
01:57:01,428 --> 01:57:03,828
Maafkan aku, anakku.

682
01:57:04,928 --> 01:57:06,828
Bukan lycan pelakunya.

683
01:57:08,928 --> 01:57:10,728
Tapi kau.

684
01:57:17,928 --> 01:57:19,828
Tinggalkan kami.

685
01:57:38,428 --> 01:57:40,828
Bagaimana kau menuntut kepercayaanku...

686
01:57:40,928 --> 01:57:43,328
jika tahu kau yang bunuh keluargaku?

687
